dc_title_s: Sketch of the recent discoveries on the northern coast of America by Daptain McClintock R.N. in search of Sir John Franklin
dc_description_s: 1 map : hand col. ; 48 x 36 cm., folded in cover 17 x 10 cm.|Relief shown by hachures.|Includes inset map showing the probable route of the Franklin Expedition.|Shows the routes of other search expeditions and places where where relics of the Franklin Expedition have been found.
